Submissions:
=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D

Abstracts should be in English, and up to four pages long. The submission=
=20
format is PDF.

Papers will be reviewed by members of the programme committee. The review=
s=20
are not anonymous.

Accepted papers may be up to 6 pages long. The final full papers should b=
e in=20
the format specified for the LREC proceedings: see the "Author's Kit" at =

http://www.lrec-conf.org/lrec2006/breve.php3?id_breve=3D3

Each submitted abstract should include: title; author(s); affiliation(s),=
=20
together with the contact author's e-mail address, postal address, teleph=
one=20
and fax numbers.

Abstracts should be submitted online in PDF format at:

        http://www.easychair.org/SALTMIL2006

The deadline for submission is February 27th.


